{"tid":831041,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南太鉉鄭恩地爭相solo，iKON與NCT回歸，可惜碰上了IU與一位無緣","createTime":"2018-09-21T15:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T14:39:27.000Z","uid":34643,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1309b0ee6c8618b2bf3646c3b2727e31ce735689","tid":831041,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2379196029,1982913425&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=553&amp;h=311&amp;s=64D813D51D7A5A130800915F03008071\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss0.baidu.com%2F6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D2379196029%2C1982913425%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D553%26h%3D311%26s%3D64D813D51D7A5A130800915F03008071&h=b635b197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在十月份南韓很多歌手都將回歸，那時候一位之爭一定會很激烈吧，十月或將成為歌手們的戰爭月了，作為winner的前隊員，南太鉉這次回歸，專輯准備的是適合秋天的性感歌曲，不知道IC們是否會為他應援呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=282736201,2416536846&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=553&amp;h=369&amp;s=B12FD0140A39729E848614D7030050B8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss1.baidu.com%2F6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D282736201%2C2416536846%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D553%26h%3D369%26s%3DB12FD0140A39729E848614D7030050B8&h=1add084b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李洪基以個人solo身份回歸，這次也是他時隔三年的再次回歸，歌迷們也是非常期待。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ss2.baidu.com/6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=3334606571,1592696593&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=552&amp;h=345&amp;s=96B0798746FA4FB1CCAD6816030050A2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss2.baidu.com%2F6ONYsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D3334606571%2C1592696593%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D552%26h%3D345%26s%3D96B0798746FA4FB1CCAD6816030050A2&h=6bb1bac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSM家的男團NCT，首張正規專輯將會在十月發行，作為EXO的師弟，SM力捧的男團，粉絲們也是十分期待這次的回歸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ss1.baidu.com/6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=3288818761,953423559&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=554&amp;h=369&amp;s=2340D91574B2F590550C4DE503008023\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss1.baidu.com%2F6ONXsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D3288818761%2C953423559%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D554%26h%3D369%26s%3D2340D91574B2F590550C4DE503008023&h=8fbfac78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApink的成員鄭恩地，這次她是以個人solo的身份回歸。此次專輯一共八首歌，她參與了其中七首歌的制作，可見她對這張專輯也是傾注了非常多的心血。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2501444655,1576410056&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=554&amp;h=369&amp;s=40505F944F7B7E805AC005CB0300F0B0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss0.baidu.com%2F6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D2501444655%2C1576410056%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D554%26h%3D369%26s%3D40505F944F7B7E805AC005CB0300F0B0&h=14f3e176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYG家以怪物新人為標志出道的組合iKON，在YG發專輯還有回歸都是一件不容易的事情，因為楊社長真的是很能拖。這次回歸康妮們也是等待了許久吧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ss0.baidu.com/6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq/it/u=2944708422,1642180255&amp;fm=175&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=554&amp;h=554&amp;s=97A3FB079E3A429CD40D48BC0300E010\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fss0.baidu.com%2F6ONWsjip0QIZ8tyhnq%2Fit%2Fu%3D2944708422%2C1642180255%26fm%3D175%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D554%26h%3D554%26s%3D97A3FB079E3A429CD40D48BC0300E010&h=38f104e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後要說的就是IU李知恩了，很多粉絲知道她也要十月份回歸，加入到此次的歌謠大戰中。紛紛表示十月份回歸的歌手們都要敗給她了。畢竟IU的人氣在韓國不是開玩笑的，而且她每次回歸都特別受關注，網友發言：不用爭，反正都會輸給IU。"},{"pid":"4063acfdcd299785e26e23110219e9309398c1ef","tid":831041,"uid":56701,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T15:27:47.000Z","msg":"好想咀啖恩地...再對佢出招龍爪手...我諗佢都應該會好享受...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我只係想講:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">恩 地  真  係  好  撚  正  呀!</span></div></em></strong></span>"},{"pid":"38871eb1357f26781c1ad7e812ee738e15a572f8","tid":831041,"